<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s ease; /* Smooth hover transition */
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #f0eded; /* Hover color: light gray */
        }

        /* Main Content */
        main {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            height: 75vh;
        }

        main h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #363637; /* Default blue color */
            transition: color 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition on hover */
        }
        main p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #444;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .info-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .info-section p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/Product">Products</a>
            <a href="/Contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h2>Welcome to the Home Page</h2>
        <div class="info-section">
            <p>We offer a wide range of products to suit your needs.</p>
            <p>Feel free to browse and reach out with any questions!</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/man-working-laptop-boss-watching_74855-10921.jpg?t=st=1736585894~exp=1736589494~hmac=8369d42d62885f528c51957ad7e0cfbb98c8fb857f83cf8d63b7ee5f34bdede2&w=740" height="300" width="450" alt="">
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 My Website</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
